isa parixqSya ko xeKawe hue viBinna SoXakarwAoM xvArA kqwrima buxXi ke kRewra Ora xqRtikoNa ko pariBARiwa karane ke rUpa meM viBinna vyAKyAoM kA prayoga kiyA gayA hE.
